-2 ②本院撤銷改判無罪","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TCHM/110%2c%e4%b8%8a%e8%a8%b4%2c984%2c20211006%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TCHM,110,上訴,984,20211006,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"上訴","JNO":"984","JDATE":"20211006","JTITLE":"違反毒品危害防制條例等"}